y be copyrighted.  Responsibility for making an independent legal assessment of an item and securing any necessary permissions ultimately rests with persons desiring to use the item.</p>\n<p>The NEH awardee responsible for producing each digital object is presented in the Chronicling America page display, below the page image  \u2013 e.g. Image produced by the Library of Congress. For more information on current NDNP awardees, see <a href=\"https://www.loc.gov/ndnp/listawardees.html\">https://www.loc.gov/ndnp/listawardees.html</a>.</p>\n<p>For more information on Library of Congress policies and disclaimers regarding rights and reproductions, see <a href=\"https://www.loc.gov/homepage/legal.html\">https://www.loc.gov/homepage/legal.html</a></p>"], "score": 13.96732, "shard": "04", "shelf_id": "sn98026438, 1945-08-31, Edition 1", "site": ["chroniclingamerica"], "source_group": "ndnp/fu", "source_modified": "2000-01-01T12:00:00Z", "subject": ["newspapers", "hernando county (fla.)", "hernando county", "brooksville", "hernando", "brooksville (fla.)", "united states", "florida"], "subject_headings": ["Brooksville (Fla.)--Newspapers", "Hernando County (Fla.)--Newspapers", "Florida--Brooksville", "Florida--Hernando County", "United States--Florida--Hernando--Brooksville"], "subjects": [{"brooksville": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:brooksville&fo=json"}, {"brooksville (fla.)": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:brooksville+%28fla.%29&fo=json"}, {"florida": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:florida&fo=json"}, {"hernando": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:hernando&fo=json"}, {"hernando county": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:hernando+county&fo=json"}, {"hernando county (fla.)": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:hernando+county+%28fla.%29&fo=json"}, {"newspapers": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:newspapers&fo=json"}, {"united states": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:united+states&fo=json"}], "timestamp": "2026-01-28T09:13:57.815Z", "title": "The Brooksville sun (Brooksville, Fla.), August 31, 1945", "type": ["issue"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/sn98026438/1945-08-31/ed-1/"}, "locations": null, "method": "mets_filesec", "more_like_this": [{"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/sn98026438/"], "batch": ["fu_lantana_ver01"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1932", "description": ["Weekly Vol. 1, no. 1 (Mar. 4, 1932-v. 27, no. 11 (Apr. 16, 1959). Also issued on microfilm from the Univesity of Florida. Merged with: Brooksville journal, to form: Brooksville sun-journal. Brooksville journal (DLC)sn 95047246 (OCoLC)33425264 Brooksville sun-journal (DLC)sn 95047247 (OCoLC)33425265"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-06-05T18:25:17.596Z", "group": ["newspaper-titles", "ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn98026438/", "image_url": [], "index": 4, "language": ["english"], "latlong": [28.554895, -82.387858], "location": ["hernando county", "hernando", "brooksville", "united states", "florida"], "location_str": "", "lonlat": [-82.387858, 28.554895], "number": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/sn98026438/1932-03-04/ed-1/", "sn95047247", "online resource", "1130", "hernando cnty libr syst", "sn98026438", "40537331", "1", "sn95047246", "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn98026438/1959-04-16/ed-1/", "original", "2025-05-23t21:30:26", "2026-04-13t21:30:13"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "partof": ["chronicling america", "the brooksville sun (brooksville, fla.) 1932-1959", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries", "serial and government publications division"], "publication_frequency": ["weekly"], "score": 88.17309, "shelf_id": "http://lccn.loc.gov/sn98026438", "site": ["chroniclingamerica", "usnd"], "subject": ["newspapers", "hernando county (fla.)", "hernando county", "brooksville", "hernando", "brooksville (fla.)", "united states", "florida"], "timestamp": "2026-07-18T09:39:13.128Z", "title": "The Brooksville sun", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/sn98026438/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2025239190/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1927", "dates": ["[1927 TO 1959]"], "description": ["Weekly Began in 1927. Tampa morning tribune, August 4, 1927, p. 4. Ceased with: Vol. 31, no. 37 (Apr. 16, 1959). Vol. 1, nos. 32-33 repeated by issues for: Mar. 1-8 and 15-22, 1928. Volume numbering erroneously changes from vol. IX, no. 30 (Feb. 27, 1936) to vol. XI, no. 31 (Mar. 5, 1936). Volume number does not change between issues: vol. XIV, no. 52 (Aug. 3, 1939) and vol. XIV, no. 1 (Aug. 10, 1939). Issues for Oct. 12, 19, 26, and Nov. 2, 1939, respectively, called vol. XIV, no. 10, vol. XV, no. 11, vol. XVI, no. 12, and vol. XIII, no. 13. Merged with: Brooksville sun, to form: Brooksville sun-journal. Vol. 1, no. 24 (Jan. 5, 1928); title from banner (loc.gov, viewed Oct. 20, 2025). Vol. 31, no. 37 (Apr. 16, 1959) (viewed Oct. 20, 2025). Brooksville sun Brooksville sun-journal (DLC) 2025239191 (OCoLC)1545792124"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:38:18.656Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2025239190/", "image_url": [], "index": 5, "language": ["english"], "location": ["hernando county", "hernando", "brooksville", "united states", "florida"], "number": ["2025239190", "2025239189", "2025239191", "online resource", "1545792193", "2026-04-13t21:30:13"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "partof": ["serial and government publications division", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries", "the brooksville journal (brooksville, fla.) 1927-1959 [online resource]"], "publication_frequency": ["weekly"], "score": 78.61508, "shelf_id": "AN2.F6.B78 J6", "site": ["usnd"], "subject": ["newspapers", "hernando county (fla.)", "hernando county", "hernando", "brooksville", "brooksville (fla.)", "united states", "florida"], "timestamp": "2026-05-26T21:15:09.430Z", "title": "The Brooksville journal", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/2025239190/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2025239191/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1959", "dates": ["[1959 TO 1963]"], "description": ["Weekly Began with: Vol. 31, no. 38 (Apr. 23, 1959); ceased with: vol. 33, no. 33 (Mar. 7, 1963). Vol. 34, nos. <7>-52 (Sept. <14>, 1961-July 26, 1962) incorrectly called vol. 33, nos. <7>-52; vol. 35, nos. 1-33 (Aug. 2, 1962-Mar. 7, 1963) incorrectly called vol. 33, nos. 1-33. Vol. 31, no. 39 (Apr. 30, 1959); title from banner (loc.gov, viewed Oct. 20, 2025). Vol. 33, no. 33 (Mar. 7, 1963) (viewed Oct. 20, 2025). Sun-journal (Brooksville, Fla. : 1963)"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:38:18.656Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2025239191/", "image_url": [], "index": 6, "language": ["english"], "location": ["hernando county", "hernando", "brooksville", "united states", "florida"], "number": ["2025239190", "2025239191", "online resource", "1545792124", "2026-04-13t21:30:13"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "other_title": ["Sun-journal"], "partof": ["the brooksville sun-journal (brooksville, fla.) 1959-1963 [online resource]", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries", "serial and government publications division"], "publication_frequency": ["weekly"], "score": 78.61508, "shelf_id": "AN2.F6.B78 S86", "site": ["usnd"], "subject": ["newspapers", "hernando county (fla.)", "hernando county", "brooksville", "hernando", "brooksville (fla.)", "united states", "florida"], "timestamp": "2026-05-26T21:15:09.430Z", "title": "The Brooksville sun-journal", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/2025239191/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/sn95047246/"], "batch": ["fu_jennings_ver01"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1